(77747,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Donate to taverns across the Dragon Isles to cover the tab!',63305),
(79173,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ihr habt deutlich mehr wiedererlangt, als wir uns erhoffen konnten. Ich habe einige der überschüssigen Dinge beiseite gelegt, damit Ihr sie haben könnt.',63305),
(79196,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'For services rendered and services yet to be rendered, accept this with The Weaver\'s compliments.',62748),
(80311,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ah, another student of the skies. Welcome to the Arboretum.',63305),
(80592,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'May your chosen patron favor you, as you have them.',61609),
(80670,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You have big talent for causing good trouble! Good good!\n\nTake these!',61609),
(81510,1,25,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Mit dieser Maschine könnt Ihr Euch auf ganz Khaz Algar bewegen. Wir geben Euch Bescheid, wenn wir neue dafür Teile haben.\n\nDa das nun geklärt wäre: ab in die Tiefen!',62876),
(81514,604,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Das hat uns ganz schön was eingebracht! Wollt Ihr Euch noch mehr amüsieren?',62876),
(82296,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ah, the Catalyst. It\'s a marvel that even words struggle to capture. \n\nPicture this, young one. Long before our city\'s foundations were laid, Titans roamed this land. Masters of the innovation, they forged wonders beyond imagination. And amidst their great works, they crafted the Catalyst.\n\nAnd now its very power belongs to you.',62876),
(82356,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Task completed. The Council rewards you for assisting with earthen reunification.',63163),
(82678,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Die sind perfekt! Bei diesen Teilen ist die Korrosion minimal. Wir sollten sämtliche Informationen retten können, die sie enthalten!\n\nJetzt legen wir seit langem vergrabenes Wissen frei, $p!',62876),
(82706,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Got tae see some nice places today. That\'s always good. Gets the ol\' heart pumpin\'.',63305),
(83333,4,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The machine continues in its duties once again.\n\nThank you again for your assistance.',62876),
(83366,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'News has come to me of your deeds among my people. Your name is spoken by earthen far and wide.',62748),
(83436,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Wenbrandt sent me the word. Well done. \n\nHere is your reward.',61122),
(83495,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Gut gemacht!\n\nNicht das, was ich erwartet hatte, aber ich muss sagen, der Schnurrbart hat mir sehr gut gefallen!',63305),
(83496,603,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ein paar Problemchen, aber nichts, was nicht durch gute, altmodische Teamarbeit gemeistert werden konnte! Wir waren großartig!',63305),
(83738,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Keep up the good good!\n\nThe Weaver also asks us to give you her \"compliments,\" but I find no \"compliments\" in here.\n\nMaybe I ate them? Apologies!',62748),
(83739,5,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Here! Accept these gifts as a tribute to your strength!\n\nIgitith ik tak\'na!',62748),
(83740,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The Vizier\'s compliments should be a more than sufficient gift for you...\n\nBut I suppose these goods would simply go to waste if not for his generosity. Take them. Be grateful.\n\nAnd do try to remain alive, overcrawler.',62748),
(83771,1022,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Gute Arbeit. Ich gebe Euch Bescheid, wenn ich noch mehr Unterstützung brauche.',63163),
(84305,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Donate to taverns across Khaz Algar to cover the tab!',63305),
