(84316,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Donate to taverns across Khaz Algar to cover the tab!',63305),
(84365,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ich habe gehört, dass sich Verstärkung der Insel nähert. Ihr kennt Khaz Algar in- und auswendig. Sie werden euer Wissen brauchen.',62876),
(84370,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Astounding! This is what I\'ve been missing. \n\nThe map Finley found is a cipher. But this key, it\'s incomplete... If you find any more out there, please bring them to me. I will decipher this map, or my name isn\'t Elise Starseeker.',63305),
(84371,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Xal\'atath war eine mächtige Waffe und... gesprächige Präsenz.',62876),
(84776,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ihr habt überlebt! Großartig!',63163),
(84779,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ich glaube, die Informationen, die meine Lehrensucherkollegen und ich gefunden haben, sind vollkommen neu. Was ihre Bedeutung betrifft, bin ich mir noch unsicher, aber vielleicht könnt Ihr das ja entscheiden.',62876),
(84782,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ihr seid auserwählt, so bemitleidenswert Ihr auch seid. Ihr solltet dankbar sein.',62876),
(84784,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ich habe keine Zweifel, dass Lord N\'Zoth diese Xal\'atath auch ohne die Hilfe seiner Gebrüder vernichten könnte, hätte sie uns nicht derartig infiltriert.',62876),
(84789,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Welche Bedeutung hatten die letzten Worte von Xal\'atath an N\'Zoth? Sah sie ihre zukünftige Zusammenarbeit voraus?\n\nWar das von Anfang an ihr Plan?',62876),
(84996,273,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Das hier scheint ein passender Ort zu sein, meinem verstorbenen Ehemann zu gedenken, Rhonin.\n\nWir sollten mit der Zeremonie fortfahren.',64978),
(84997,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Uff... <Vereesa krümmt sich.>\n\nTruppen der Leere... greifen an. Wieso hier... jetzt?',64978),
(85005,66,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I see you received my message $p, wonderful! We can always use more capable soldiers among the ranks of the Flame\'s Radiance.',62876),
(85244,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'We did it! Hah! \n\nThat\'ll show the world not tae mess with us! \n\nAnd tae never try stealin\' me hat again! \n\nAh... it feels so good tae have ye back. \n\nHere. Take me spare hat. It didn\'t feel right tae wear it while the other one was missin\'.',61967),
(85648,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'That\'s one less issue to deal with.',62876),
(85649,1022,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Commendable work within the Waterworks.',62876),
(85664,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Mir ist zu Ohren gekommen, dass jemand den Machenschaften des Ordens der Nacht ein Ende gesetzt hat. Gute Arbeit.',63163),
(85871,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ihr seid mit dem Staub der Schatten bedeckt wie das Blut Eurer Feinde. Gut.',62876),
(86151,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The treacherous path of the Burned Bridge will be available to you if you wish to tread it.',62493),
(86152,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The path of the Daredevil is available to you if you dare.',62493),
(86153,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The risks at the edges of your sanity will now manifest if you so choose to engage them.',61265),
(86154,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'As my madness and torment is not enough, feel free to invite even more pain in the future.',61265),
(86155,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Taking a step towards the Longest Night is already acknowledging the sanity you have lost. Do you risk the rest on such a fools errand?',61265),
(86365,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Remarkable!\n\nKeep in mind I can only transmute Crests into a higher tier when you have outgrown their usefulness, and it will be a costly process. Thank you for all of your help!',62876),
(86503,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I saw your fight, good stuff. Here\'s your prize purse. Pleasure doing business.\n\nFeel free to sign up again. I\'ll remember to not bet against you next time.',61265),
(86706,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You are just in time as always! Let us speak of what brings me here.',61265),
(86801,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Satiated in the blood of multitudes now and forever. For our ranks will be endless and consume the world.',61265),
(87328,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent! There is no time to lose.',61265),
(87329,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'It\'s alright, $n. You are back. You\'ve done well. Remember, this was just a memory of a vision. \n\nWhile we will keep you safe from the past, the danger we are all in from the Void is still very real in the present.',62876),
(87332,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hello there, $c. So you\'re our latest test subject--I mean, the one to revisit the visions of the past? \n\nI hear you have some displaced corrupted mementos from your last trip. \n\nPerfect! I\'ll show you what they can do.',62876),
(87335,603,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The more echoes you make, the more mementos it\'ll take. \n\nIf you ever want to know how much you need for the next one, talk to me. I\'ll figure it out. \n\nThose visions are so creepy--but together I know we\'ll succeed, $c. The Void stands no chance against us.',62876),
(87336,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'As Augermu told you--with the help of the hourglass, you can now enter the Horrific Visions as much as you like. \n\nOne more thing--we have identified some key memories within each of the visions. Through them, you will find additional boons specific to that vision that allow you to remain longer and explore more. \n\nI will add descriptions in the vision\'s Heart Chamber to help you find or unlock these boons.',62876),
(87342,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Honor the Isle of Dorn flame.',61609),
(87355,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Honor the Hallowfall flame.',61609),
(87356,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Honor the Azj-Kahet flame.',61609),
(87357,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Honor the Ringing Deeps flame.',61609),
(87417,1005,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Thank you for bringing all people of Khaz Algar a glimmer of hope.',62438),
(87419,1005,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'There are fewer shadows in the world thanks to your efforts.',61967),
(87475,1005,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ein weiterer Sieg über die Sureki! Mereldars Verteidiger werden sich um die restlichen Neruber außerhalb der Mauern kümmern.\n\nDas Volk von Mereldar steht in Eurer Schuld.',63305),
(87477,1005,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Gut gemacht, $gSoldat:Soldatin;! Der Schwarm wurde fürs Erste verlangsamt.\n\nZweifelsohne nähern sich uns just in diesem Moment noch mehr von den Biestern aus den Tiefen von Azj-Kahet.\n\nWenn sie auftauchen, werden die Strahlen der Flamme gewappnet sein!',63305),
(87480,1005,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Eure Bemühungen, die Belagerung von Dunelles Güte zu vereiteln, waren ein Segen für ganz Heilsturz.\n\nWäre der Dämmersturm erloschen, hätte tiefe Finsternis den östlichen Teil von Heilsturz verschlungen.\n\nHabt Dank, $n.',63305),
(87550,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I was right, right? The fans went wild! You\'re really earning a name for yourself!',61609),
(87551,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I like your style! Here\'s your prize, and a little something extra for advertising the show.',61609),
(87552,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You fight with style! You should practice your autograph -- I hear some of the viewers are forming a fan club around you.',61609),
(87553,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Loved the act, $N. Here\'s your prize purse.\n\nDid I see you drink a Can of Amps during the fight? Thanks! Way to get that product placement on camera!',61609),
(87554,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Wow. Just...wow. I thought you were a goner for a second there, then I realized it was all an act for you. You get it.\n\nTake care of yourself, $N. And if you ever wanna stop saving the world, you\'ll have a bright future in showbiz.',61609),
(88803,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You may call upon this aid for any vision.',62876),
(88808,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I knew I could trust in you to complete such a feat.',61609),
(88903,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Be prepared to face the wrath of your enemies should you don this mask.',61265),
(88916,66,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Sich in die finsteren Tiefen von Azj-Kahet zu wagen, ist keine leichte Aufgabe, $gSoldat:Soldatin;.\n\nEure Arbeit dort unten hat dem Volk von Heilsturz eine kleine Verschnaufpause verschafft.',63163),
(89039,1005,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Thanks, pal. Undermine is a mess right now. We\'ll take all the help we can get.\n\nAnd hey, a deal\'s a deal. Here\'s what we owe.',61609),
(89223,1,1,273,0,0,300,300,0,'A remnant of Azeroth from a time of conflict and strife. Such a troubled artifact has no place in the timeways, thank you for returning it.',61967),
(89263,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You $p? Got something for you.',61609),
(89332,4,-1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Der Heiligen Flamme sei Dank für Eure Unterstützung. Der Krieg geht weiter, doch wenigstens ist die Schlacht gewonnen.',63163),
(89349,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Eure beispielhafte Hilfe ist nicht unbemerkt geblieben, $n. Ich hoffe, dass diese Belohnung Euch gute Dienste leistet.',63163),
(89404,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'$n! You surely are a welcome sight to see on this dark day. Our teleportation spell went awry and now the Legion is invading Dalaran.',63660),
(89405,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well met, $n, and splendid work. You took the pressure off us just long enough to get a handle on this whole debacle.',63660),
(89406,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I think this is magnificent!\n\nYou\'re the perfect control group to test our theories on the importance of artifacts in the grand scheme of the flow of timelines.',63660),
(89407,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'A fine collection of epoch objects.',63660),
(89408,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'These threads contain traces of potential epoch energy. To access their power we\'ll need to infuse them into a stabilizing material, such as infinite bronze, in order to anchor them in place.\n\nThey\'ll lose some of their potency, but at least they will be sufficient for our needs.',63660),
(89409,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Now that you have infinite bronze we can get you an artifact in order to properly carry out our tests.\n\nThen you\'ll have no problem living up to your own legend, $n.',63660),
(89411,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Good. Good. You do well. Artifact grows stronger. Almost as strong as Erus.\n\n<Erus laughs at his own boast.>',63660),
(89412,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I can sense the power emanating from your artifact from here. Good.\n\nI\'ve also noted that it hasn\'t fractured under the power load yet. Also good.\n\nLet me just make a note of that for Moratari\'s records. Very good.',63660),
(89413,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Bronze can be spent at the infinite bazaar on many pretty things.\n\nWhenever you find junk, just summon the Unraveling Sands.\n\nJunk goes in, pretty bronze comes out.\n\nIs convenient, yes?',63660),
(89414,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'It has been a hard day, $n, but our resolve is soon to be rewarded.\n\nWith the Legion distracted by your timely heroics, I was able to stretch out my arcane power and divine the mastermind behind the Legion incursion into our beloved city.',63660),
(89415,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'We make a good team, $n.\n\nThe Kirin Tor will handle the remaining Legion forces from here. For now my attention must turn to restoring the wards to their full strength.',63660),
(89416,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Moratari has kept me apprised of your endeavors in this timeline, $n.\n\nKnow that I am pleased.\n\nDalaran will recover in time. Speaking of, I will accelerate the timeline until after the cleanup is complete.',63660),
(89417,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'As you can see, $n, there are many minds at work here in the infinite dragonflight. Minds that are all working to answer some pressing questions.\n\nWhat knowledge can we gain to prepare us for even greater threats?\n\nWould we have triumphed if things had been worse?\n\nWhat are the implications of Sargeras\'s sword being plunged into Azeroth, and was it the artifacts that saved Azeroth or something else?\n\nEr, I mean... Forget I said anything. What sword?',63660),
(89418,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'And here we are, back where it all started.\n\nIn a moment a messenger will come looking for you and your legend will begin to unfold.\n\n<Moratari smiles broadly at you, beaming with excitement.>\n\nAren\'t you excited? I know I am.\n\nOh, and if you need anything, just come by the Infinite Bazaar. We\'re always waiting.\n\nGood luck!',63660),
(89465,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Your name is on the minds of the people, and is shared around the fire. The greater your legend becomes, the more powerful your name will be. But does the power of one\'s name eclipse that of the artifact they wield? This is the burning question.',64270),
(89466,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The sum strength of a group of timerunners armed with potent artifacts is greater than that of the individuals. Much greater than anticipated. Intriguing.',64978),
(89467,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The sum strength of a group of timerunners armed with potent artifacts is greater than that of the individuals. Much greater than anticipated. Intriguing.',64978),
(89468,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You have no idea how happy this will make Moratari.',64978),
(89469,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You have no idea how happy this will make Moratari.',64877),
(89493,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Welcome, cadet! Glad to have you here. \n\nNo time like the present to get in there. Fight the Sureki with everything you\'ve got--we\'re counting on you.',62876),
(89516,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Very good results. Exceeds expectations.',64978),
