(89591,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The sum strength of a group of timerunners armed with potent artifacts is greater than that of the individuals. Much greater than anticipated. Intriguing.',64877),
(89592,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Teamwork makes the dream work, or so they say. It would appear that the rhyme carries truth to it. Hmmm.\n\n<Eternus pauses for a moment in thought.>\n\nI wonder what other rhymes carry such power. That bears some future experimentation.',64978),
