(89681,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The sum strength of a group of timerunners armed with potent artifacts is greater than that of the individuals. Much greater than anticipated. Intriguing.',64978),
(89682,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Teamwork makes the dream work, or so they say. It would appear that the rhyme carries truth to it. Hmmm.\n\n<Eternus pauses for a moment in thought.>\n\nI wonder what other rhymes carry such power. That bears some future experimentation.',64877),
(89683,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The sum strength of a group of timerunners armed with potent artifacts is greater than that of the individuals. Much greater than anticipated. Intriguing.',64978),
(90096,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'A single heroic act can turn the tide. A single whisper of hope can turn back despair. This is what gives legends their power.',64978),
(90097,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The power you and your artifact possess were able to halt a Legion invasion. But was it you, or the artifact you wield, that is responsible? On that I will require more information.',64877),
(90098,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Just as I predicted. You were able to stop a massive Legion invasion. It was not you, or your artifact that did this. Rather it was the combination of both that won the day.',64877),
(90099,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well done, $p. Moratari will be overjoyed to see these new data points.',64270),
(90100,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well done, $p. Moratari will be overjoyed to see these new data points.',63834),
(90101,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'A fascinating outcome, $p. This will shed some much needed light on our research.',64877),
(90102,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Your legend has grown, $p. The timeline reverberates with not just the substance of your deeds, but it compounds as it impacts those around you. This has been a most fruitful addition to our research.',64978),
(90108,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You have quite the collection now, $p. All that remains to be seen is whether you prefer one artifact over the other.',63834),
(90109,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Good. Nothing dramatic occured when you gathered the residual time motes. If you start to feel anything strange, do let us know though.',64877),
(90110,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Moratari will be elated to see so many test samples. Thank you for your diligence.',64978),
(90112,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well done, $p. Moratari will be overjoyed to see these new data points.',64978),
(90113,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Impressive. I can sense your power. This is a most critical addition to our research.',64978),
(90114,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Impressive. I can sense your power. This is a most critical addition to our research.',64270),
(90115,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Impressive. I can sense your power. This is a most critical addition to our research.',64877),
(90659,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Intriguing. This artifact\'s potential has been deepened, perhaps by the fraying of this timeline. It can harness more power than any incarnation of it that I have yet encountered.\n\nLet me record that data point for Moratari.\n\nOh, important reminder--don\'t forget to recover the bronze simulacrum later or things might get... funky.\n\nAnd lastly, maybe don\'t mention to people how you got that. It could ruin the experiment.',63660),
(90701,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Way to go, $n. You have to show those bombs who\'s boss, you know?',61265),
(90719,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Yes, by combining this residue with the displaced corrupted mementos I can... yeah just like so... and then with a bit of my bronze magic... there. Done.\n\nNow that I have a working knowledge I can also make more if you bring me additional displaced corrupted mementos. I will see if I can refine the process anymore. Check back with me later.',61265),
(90731,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ok, this is promising... the coagulate catalyzes slower so the increased corruption is more contained... yes, this allows a higher yield of corrupted material without any negative side effects.\n\nAlas, I cannot keep it stable for long. These effects will not last. I am sorry adventurer but we should take advantage of the effects while we can. \n\nAgain, if you bring me additional displaced corrupted mementos I can make you more of these greater corruptions.',61265),
(90759,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Thank you for coming, $p. The Twilight\'s Blade cannot be allowed to roam our cities.',65655),
(90776,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'',63305),
(90778,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'',63305),
(90870,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ah, ye\'ve done it! The cooks will be pleased.',63305),
(90879,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ah, I can smell the pretzels from here. Ye\'ve cooked up a spread that\'ll keep even the pickiest dwarves satisfied!',63305),
(90885,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Das sind... ziemlich viele Kürbisse.\n\nIch denke, unser Bauernfreund sollte sie zurück nach Hammerfall bringen. Verstärkungen der Horde sollten bereits dort sein.',64978),
(90886,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Wie ich mir gedacht habe.\n\nIch kann das kaum entziffern.',64978),
(90887,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Das sollte helfen, die Kreaturen zu vertreiben. Ohne einen Anführer werden sie flüchten, wenn die Verstärkungen von Allianz und Horde erscheinen.',64978),
(90888,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Das sieht schlimm aus, aber wir werden schon damit fertig.',64978),
(90892,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'<The skies are a little clearer now. The infinites might be interested in trading with this extra bronze I\'ve collected.>',63704),
(90893,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Die Belagerung ist vorbei. Wir haben ihren Anführer umstellt.',64978),
(90895,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ohne die Katapulte sollten die Soldaten von Stromgarde die Oberhand gewinnen können.',64978),
(90896,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Die Belagerung ist vorüber. Das Arathihochland wird nun hoffentlich wieder einigermaßen zur Ruhe kommen.',64978),
(90898,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hammerfall wird sich schnell erholen und stärker als zuvor aus dieser Belagerung hervorgehen.',64978),
(90901,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'As you gather infinite power do not forget to focus it into your artifact.\n\nThe more power you invest, the swifter you will gather more infinite power and grow your artifact\'s legend--and your own.',63660),
(90969,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'$n, these consoles are bein\' overloaded by the titan\'s presence. If we can defeat them and secure titan discs, I think we can use \'em to empower the console to grant ye boons within the space. The boons can aid you in pushing back these rogue titan constructs.',61967),
(90970,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Did ye find the shards? While ye were away, I remembered I\'d found some on my visit to that location. Ye should find them in a pouch I hid next to the console.',61967),
(90971,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'My remote console shows that there was a change. The overcharged console is funnelin\' excess energy to a new node. This should grant ye that node\'s power when venturin\' intae other areas where the titan constructs have emerged.\n\nWe\'ll use the titan force\'s own energy against \'em!',61967),
(91009,595,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Attach the device. Yes! The device is powered on. \n\nOkay... If I just start the initialization sequence... and it\'s up. There are already two discs inside. And the menu will list areas where other miniature titan discs can be found. I\'m thinkin\' I can improve the device, but I need time. Find me later and see.',62876),
(91026,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Here, yes... With that information I can make some final tweaks. And adding this directive...\n\nAh! That should do it. If you insert this into yer durable information storage container, it should update the effectiveness of the device\'s, um... effects.',62876),
(91030,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hmm, as I suspected. Yes... I need to adjust this here... done.\n\nThe good news is that this upgrade will nae make yer belt explode! I thought there was a small chance, but no longer. Yer data proved that I set the power too high. So... good thing I had ye do tha\' extra check, right?',62876),
(91031,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The data from that last excursion provided what I needed for another upgrade. But this is the last upgrade we can do for the belt, unless we want a major meltdown. Of course a meltdown would tell us a lot about the design...\n\nMa always said, \"Dagran! If yer gonna destroy ancient, irreplaceable artifacts, destroy yer own.\" So this is the last upgrade.\n\nHere is the last upgrade card. Thank ye for yer help. I hope we get a chance to experiment more in the future!',64270),
(91033,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Their behavior seems mostly unchanged. This is very frustrating. Also if yer data is correct, it looks like they might be calmin\' down. \n\nWe will have tae see if this observation is true. And here is some additional gear that we have collected. I hope it has served ye well over the course of our scientific endeavors!',61967),
(91035,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Wow! Tha\' drop off is huge. If this holds steady, these constructs could be gone soon! \n\nWe still don\'t know what prompted them to come out! What if we never know? I hope that they return.\n\nOh, no! I don\'t want them tae mess things up. I just hate tae leave this unsolved. \n\nAt least we will be more prepared if we do see them again. Thank ye for yer help, $n. I\'ve checked the numbers and yer belt should still work, even if the constructs do retreat. \n\nAnd one last box of supplies for yer help.',61967),
(91038,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'We appreciate your interest in aiding us.\n\nShards of our timeline have made their way into your world. It is a place more grim and dark than your own, where some villains became heroes and some heroes never had the chance.\n\nHelp us locate these hellish fragments out of time and return them to their rightful place, and we will provide you with armors tempered by the fires of our world.\n\nAnd should you find any Treasure Goblins that lurk in your world, we implore you to slay the abominations.',61609),
(91041,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'This present looks like it has been shaken a few times. The tag on it reads:$b$bTo a very special $r $c.',64978),
(91042,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'A small tag on this present reads:$b$bHappy holidays, $n!',64978),
(91061,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You are braver than I thought, $n.\n\nPlease continue to experiment. I will not let us enter dangerous futures unprepared.',63704),
(91066,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hah! I can smell those pretzels from here. You\'ve cooked up a feast fit to silence even the grumbling of dwarves!',63305),
(91067,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You\'ve done it! The cooks will be pleased.',63305),
(91068,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I\'d say you\'ve earned yourself a break and a strong brew after all that work. But don\'t go getting soft on me! Brewfest isn\'t over, and there\'s still plenty of work to be done.',63305),
(91173,66,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ihr habt einen Augenblick des Friedens für uns herausgeschunden.\n\nRuht Euch aus, doch achtet stets darauf, dass Eure Klinge geschliffen ist.',63305),
(91205,1005,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Thanks, pal. Undermine is a mess right now. We\'ll take all the help we can get.\n\nAnd hey, a deal\'s a deal. Here\'s what we owe.\n\nWe call this the jackpot reward for first time help. Check back again for more work!',61122),
(91420,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'<Om\'myuz takes a closer look at the ore.>\n\nThat is quite the intriguing rock you\'ve found. I would like to inspect it further, and any others you find. What say you to a trade?\n\nOther Cartel Om members in the Veiled Market may also be interested in trading wares, should you come across them.',62493),
(91437,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent timing, $p. Now the research can begin.',64978),
(91438,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'A single heroic act can turn the tide. A single whisper of hope can turn back despair. This is what gives legends their power.',64154),
(91439,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'The power you and your artifact possess were able to halt a Legion invasion. But was it you, or the artifact you wield, that is responsible? On that I will require more information.',64978),
(91440,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Your name is on the minds of the people, and is shared around the fire. The greater your legend becomes, the more powerful your name will be. But does the power of one\'s name eclipse that of the artifact they wield? This is the burning question.',63834),
(91443,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well done, $p. Moratari will be overjoyed to see these new data points.',64154),
(91445,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well done, $p. Moratari will be overjoyed to see these new data points.',64978),
(91446,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well done, $p. Moratari will be overjoyed to see these new data points.',64154),
(91448,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'A fascinating outcome, $p. This will shed some much needed light on our research.',64154),
(91449,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Well done, $p. Moratari will be overjoyed to see these new data points.',64154),
(91477,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hört gut zu: Wir haben neue Technologie beschafft, die Euch helfen kann, die Schattenwache zu besiegen. Macht das Beste draus.',63305),
(91481,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Zo\'ropo brings you a new weapon. Use this to feed off of the Manaforge\'s arcane radiation and turn their energies against them.',62748),
(91483,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'There are consoles inside the Manaforge that keep the flow of energy running smoothly within the facility. We\'ve cracked security on the first set of them, allowing you to turn the tables on enemies near Loom\'ithar and Soulbinder Naazindrhi. You\'ll only be able to use one, but sabotaging them should allow you an edge in battle. Good luck in there.',62748),
(91484,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Wir haben eine Schwachstelle in der Werkstatt von Schmiedeweber Araz gefunden, die Euch Zugang zu einer weiteren Konsole in der Nähe verschafft. Bleibt am Ball. Wir geben Euch Bescheid, sobald die ganze Anlage unter unserer Kontrolle ist. Viel Erfolg bei der Jagd!',63305),
(91525,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Its quality is unlike anything I\'ve ever seen! I\'ll get to work right away. Now, let\'s discuss your payment.',62493),
(91613,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'$n, you have been an excellent assistant with our research. I think you deserve a promotion.\n\nFrom now on, you will be able to take on more research assignments simultaneously.\n\nIt\'s ironic, isn\'t it, that we never seem to have enough time. Make good use of your time here. Don\'t make me regret granting you this power.',63796),
(91614,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent, Archdruid. These will do nicely.',64270),
(91631,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Your power grows stronger, $p.\n\nPlease, take this token of our gratitude for your assistance with our research. Let it echo with every you that exists in the fractures of this timeline.',63704),
(91632,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You have reached your full potential, $p. Or have you? Perhaps this is only the beginning of your journey through this epoch.\n\nPlease, take this token of our gratitude for your assistance with our research. Let it echo with every you that exists in the fractures of this timeline.',63796);
INSERT IGNORE INTO `quest_offer_reward` (`ID`, `Emote1`, `Emote2`, `Emote3`, `Emote4`, `EmoteDelay1`, `EmoteDelay2`, `EmoteDelay3`, `EmoteDelay4`, `RewardText`, `VerifiedBuild`) VALUES
(91639,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You have grown stronger, but your artifact is stronger yet.\n\nIt would appear that my hypothesis holds true--artifacts appear to be the key to protecting Azeroth.',63796),
(91721,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'I admit. I am pleasantly surprised to be proven wrong. Your power has grown and I cannot say with certainty which is the greater. You, or the weapon you wield.',63834),
(91722,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Humbling.\n\nIt is the very nature of finite existence that is the answer.\n\nMortality is the flame that shines brightest because it is free to choose a single moment of glory, rather than be burdened by the weight of eternity.\n\nChoose your moment well, $p, and nothing, not even time, will be able to stop you.',63834),
(91728,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Very intriguing.\n\nI will, of course, record that as a data point.\n\nKnowing how you decide on a course of action will inform further hypothesis.',64877),
(91729,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Fresh insights are invaluable in our efforts here, $p.\n\nThank you for sharing yours.',64270),
(91730,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Too many histories are written about the WHAT, the WHY, the HOW, and the WHEN. Other than names, however, we so rarely get to truly know the WHO.',64978),
(91757,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'There. That was not so bad after all.\n\nThis is not goodbye. It is just a pause until our next hello.\n\nI look forward to it, $p.',64877),
(91780,4,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Good tae see ye! We\'ve got plenty tae discuss.',62493),
(91781,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Right, on to that wee problem I mentioned.',62493),
(91821,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hmm, burning that pamphlet produced a very peculiar reaction from the flames.\n\n<Moratari begins taking notes, completely ignoring you.>',64978),
(91844,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'$n, you have been an excellent assistant with our research. I think you deserve a promotion.\n\nFrom now on, you will be able to take on more research assignments simultaneously.\n\nIt\'s ironic, isn\'t it, that we never seem to have enough time. Make good use of your time here. Don\'t make me regret granting you this power.',63834),
(91845,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'$n, you have been an excellent assistant with our research. I think you deserve a promotion.\n\nFrom now on, you will be able to take on more research assignments simultaneously.\n\nIt\'s ironic, isn\'t it, that we never seem to have enough time. Make good use of your time here. Don\'t make me regret granting you this power.',63906),
(91846,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'$n, you have been an excellent assistant with our research. I think you deserve a promotion.\n\nFrom now on, you will be able to take on more research assignments simultaneously.\n\nIt\'s ironic, isn\'t it, that we never seem to have enough time. Make good use of your time here. Don\'t make me regret granting you this power.',64978),
(91855,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'You are a credit to heroes everywhere. Thank you.',62748),
(91863,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Glückwunsch zu Eurem neuen Zuhause. Wir wissen, dass Ihr Euch hier sehr wohlfühlen werdet, und wir freuen uns schon darauf, Euch in der Nachbarschaft zu sehen.',64978),
(91955,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Success!\n\nIt\'s almost a shame to destroy such a beautiful replica.\n\nBut you have the real thing, so I say scrap it and rejoice at the bounty of beautiful bronze!',63704),
(91968,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ein Platz für alles, an dem alles seinen Platz hat.',64978),
(91969,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ausgezeichnete Arbeit! Jetzt sieht es hier schon mehr nach einem Zuhause aus.\n\nIch könnte Euch zwar jahrtausendelang mein Wissen näherbringen, aber ich denke, man lernt am besten, wenn man etwas selbst macht.\n\nHört nie auf zu gestalten! Hört nie auf zu erschaffen!',64978),
(92028,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hervorragende Arbeit! Jetzt sollte ich Zeit haben, den Fehler zu beheben, der ursprünglich dafür verantwortlich ist.\n\nVielleicht sollte ich einfach so tun, als wäre es Absicht gewesen, und es gut sein lassen!',64978),
(92405,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'My aunt has been having terrible visions and they are getting worse.',65299),
(92430,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent timing, $p. Now the research can begin.',63704),
(92439,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Impressive. I can sense your power. This is a most critical addition to our research.',63796),
(92440,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Impressive. I can sense your power. This is a most critical addition to our research.',63834),
(92442,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Impressive. I can sense your power. This is a most critical addition to our research.',64877),
(92563,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Fascinating, it seems as though the magic of your new accessory is capable of awakening otherwise inaccessible powers of your artifact weapon, or even enhancing them beyond their limits!\n\nI wonder if all jewelry has this same connection to your artifact weapon. Please do keep me informed of any more anomalies.',63704),
(92688,603,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'YES! Erus will scrap!',63704),
(92816,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'<Ihr seid jetzt auf dem Weg in ein neues Abenteuer!>',64978),
(92855,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'What, you think I\'m just going to give you my crafts for free?\n\n<Lidamorrutu grumbles.>\n\nI suppose that\'s exactly what I\'m going to do. Eternus\'s orders, something about speeding up the experiment.\n\nJust don\'t lose it or, worse, let Erus anywhere near it.',64877),
(93055,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Hopefully this diversion has been enlightening.',63704),
(93056,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Yes, now you are prepared.',63796),
(93112,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent progress. Here are the spoils of your victory.',63796),
(93113,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent progress. Here are the spoils of your victory.',63796),
(93114,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent progress. Here are the spoils of your victory.',63796),
(93116,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent progress. Here are the spoils of your victory.',63796),
(93117,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent progress. Here are the spoils of your victory.',63796),
(93118,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent progress. Here are the spoils of your victory.',63796),
(93120,1,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Excellent progress. Here are the spoils of your victory.',63834),
(93647,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Ihr seht wie jemand aus, der sich gut im Holzfäll\'n mach\'n würd\'.\n\nHier, ich zeig\' Euch, woran Ihr Bäume erkennt, die sich zum Fäll\'n eignen.\n\nHolz is\' für viele Dinge in Euerm Haus nützlich. Oder auch für andere Häuser, wenn Ihr was verschenk\'n oder verkauf\'n wollt. Ich wette, die alten Handwerkslehrer, von denen Ihr gelernt habt, hab\'n neue Dinge anzubiet\'n.\n\nGeht da raus un\' schaut, was sich so mach\'n lässt!',64978),
(94210,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Konntet Ihr gute Stücke für Euer Haus finden? Wir hoffen, dass uns in der Zukunft weitere Händler besuchen werden, also schaut gelegentlich vorbei!',64978),
(94379,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Wie lief die Renovierung? Hoffentlich habt Ihr nun genug Stauraum für all die Schätze, die Ihr auf Euren Abenteuern erbeutet.\n\nSchaut wieder beim Baumeister vorbei, wenn Ihr bereit für die nächste Aufwertung seid.\n\nOh, und es ist ein Brief für Euch angekommen, als Ihr unterwegs wart.',64978),
(94455,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'Macht es Euch gemütlich!',64978);
