(32257,0,0,0,0,'We are quite capable of handling this excavation. I understand the Warchief sent you, but he will get faster results if he leaves us to our work.',0),
(32318,0,0,0,0,'My herbs are the only thing keeping Vol\'jin from death. I dare not leave his side.',0),
(32319,0,0,0,0,'You have come a long way to see me, $r. Speak.',0),
(32379,0,0,0,0,'Have you found anything on the mogu?',0),
(32448,1,1,0,0,'You never know what you will find in a book. Especially an ancient pandaren one.$B$BI\'m eager to see how this Memory Wine works.',63305),
(37656,0,396,0,0,'If we\'re to defeat the Legion, we need to know exactly what they\'re up to.',63834),
(37957,0,0,0,0,'Ah, Stella. Always so quick to act. She is still young.',63834),
(38147,0,0,0,0,'Someone entangled us within a sinister spell.',63834),
(38206,0,0,0,0,'As soon as preparations are complete, we set out for Stormheim.',63834),
(38331,0,0,0,0,'Smells good, doesn\'t it?',63834),
(38412,0,0,0,0,'',63834),
(38413,0,0,0,0,'What news do you bring of my brothers and sisters?',63834),
(38460,0,0,0,0,'Yeah! Yeah! You read the contract? I made it myself. Really good binding clauses in there.',63834),
(38909,0,0,0,0,'Have you had any luck with the Rivermane?',63834),
(39305,0,1,0,0,'If there\'s any hope for those eggs hatching, they\'ll need to be returned to their nest.',63834),
(39387,0,0,0,0,'Have you had any luck with Lasan?',63834),
(39455,0,0,0,0,'Are you afraid of the dark?',63834),
(39456,0,0,0,0,'Has Torok agreed to join us?',63834),
(39990,0,0,0,0,'This shouldn\'t take long. Please do not allow them to interrupt my spell.',63834),
(40069,1,1,0,0,'What are their guts for? Well, you\'ll see. You might not like it, but you will soon find out.',63834),
(40070,1,1,0,0,'If the pilfered eggs are not recovered, the eagle may go extinct.',63834),
(40071,0,0,0,0,'Put an end to Tamer Korgrul, so that we may also put an end to the training of siege worms.',63834),
(40219,0,0,0,0,'You are learning parts of our history few outsiders have ever known.',63834),
(40227,0,6,0,0,'Why do you seek to dissuade me?',64502),
(40401,0,6,0,0,'Who are you to seek passage into Suramar?',64502),
