(42833,0,0,0,0,'',64502),
(42838,0,0,0,0,'How did your trip to the Vineyard go?',64502),
(42857,0,0,0,0,'You have found a fruit that might be of interest to me?',0),
(42865,0,0,0,0,'I miss the days when grell kept to themselves and played tricks on the night elves.',63834),
(42883,0,0,0,0,'The grell can sometimes be a terrible nuisance.',63834),
(42884,0,0,0,0,'My old bones need more rest than I would care to admit.',63834),
(43309,0,0,0,0,'Thalyssra asks much of me.',64502),
(43331,26,0,0,0,'This seems to be where the Sixtrigger brothers keep their most prized spoils.',0),
(43360,0,0,0,0,'Death is the only kindness we can give them now.',64502),
(43365,0,0,0,0,'Death and life, the same.',64502),
(43403,0,0,0,0,'Conflict rages across the Broken Isles.',64502),
(43409,0,0,0,0,'We honor you, $ct.',64502),
(43565,0,0,0,0,'Imagine firing an arrow at the sky in hopes of hitting an acorn at the far end of the forest.$B$BThis teleport will be a little harder, but I think I can do it.',64502),
(43810,0,0,0,0,'Have you eliminated the threat?',64502),
(43892,0,1,0,0,'These seals provide an additional chance at treasure in dungeons and raids, but at what cost? Your order will certainly not miss these extra resources, but I must ask: When does it end?  Will you ever stop risking others lives just to satisfy your greedy nature?\n\nYou can only obtain three seals per week.  This counts as one of those three.  Next week, I will have others.',0),
(43991,0,0,0,0,'Did you find the druidic stones? A sapling needs to be nurtured, and a candle lit with arcane fire. A tenacious guardian may only appear to one as tenacious as itself, and a ferocious hunter often camouflages itself in the shadows.',63834),
(43995,0,0,0,0,'<Valtrois does not respond. Her expression betrays a deep pain welling within.>',0),
(44004,0,6,0,0,'Have you discovered anything about the object?',64978),
(44057,0,0,0,0,'Have your champions discovered anything about the fox hunt?',0),
(44074,0,0,0,0,'Stand firm, druid.',63834),
(44075,0,0,0,0,'It takes a ferocious beast to take down another ferocious beast.',63834),
(44076,0,0,0,0,'My heart aches for those fallen to the Nightmare.',63834),
(44077,0,0,0,0,'We follow Elune\'s path.',0),
(44283,0,0,0,0,'If only Cenarius were with us, we could confront Xavius at once.',63834),
(44284,0,0,0,0,'If only Cenarius were with us, we could confront Xavius at once.',63834),
(44285,0,0,0,0,'If only Cenarius were with us, we could confront Xavius at once.',63834),
(44400,0,0,0,0,'Oh, no. Don\'t tell me something ELSE has gone wrong?!',64978),
(44486,0,0,0,0,'Oh, what\'s this one now?',0),
(44719,0,0,0,0,'We\'ve done it! Despite the initial failures, we are still in position to enter the Breach and free our comrades.',64978),
(44726,0,0,0,0,'Have you dealt with Aargoss?',64502),
(44742,0,0,0,0,'Dire news like this cannot wait.',64502),
(44752,0,0,0,0,'Did you find them?',64502),
(44753,0,0,0,0,'I need to maintain complete focus.',64502),
(44858,0,0,0,0,'We elves are long lived, but not as long lived as our prejudices it would seem.',64502),
(44874,0,1,0,0,'This ley line energy will not move itself. We must give it encouragement.',64502),
(44875,0,1,0,0,'This ritual will shake the pool of energy loose, allowing it to flow through the ley line unimpeded.',64502),
(44918,0,0,0,0,'We have no time to waste.',64502),
(44928,0,0,0,0,'Were you able to find the instigators?',64502),
(45088,0,0,0,0,'Bring me the souls of my lost Valarjar. Only then will I reward you with the blessed armor you desire.',63834),
(45260,0,0,0,0,'In time, all of the shal\'dorei will be free.',64502),
(45261,0,0,0,0,'No matter what crises come up, we must stay the course and free my people from their addiction.$B$BWe take it one day at a time.',64502),
(45262,0,0,0,0,'The message is almost ready.',64502),
(45263,0,0,0,0,'Are you ready?',64502),
(45265,0,0,0,0,'My people must be free.',64502),
(45266,0,0,0,0,'Is it done?',64502),
(45267,0,0,0,0,'I have dreamt of this moment since the day I fled.',64502),
(45268,0,0,0,0,'Are you ready?',64502),
(45269,0,0,0,0,'Even if our failure means their doom, they deserve a taste of freedom, no matter how fleeting.',64502),
(45381,0,0,0,0,'Without the talisman we must fight through the city proper.',64978),
(45382,0,0,0,0,'Without the talisman we must fight through the city proper.',64978),
(45383,0,0,0,0,'Without the talisman we must fight through the city proper.',64502),
(45413,0,0,0,0,'We can\'t risk another attack until we get to the bottom of this.',64502),
(45414,0,0,0,0,'This is deeply concerning.',64502),
(45415,0,0,0,0,'Lord Illidan led us into glorious battle against Kruul long ago. Now you must do the same.',64502),
(45863,0,0,0,0,'Are you ready?',64502),
(46244,0,0,0,0,'There is little time. Mephistroth must be defeated, and the Cathedral of the Eternal Night secured.',64502),
(46246,0,6,0,0,'Did they plead for their lives?$b$bDid they whimper as they bled away to nothingness?',64502),
(46248,0,6,0,0,'How go your efforts on the warfront?',64502),
(46250,0,6,0,0,'Are they dead yet?',64502),
(46252,0,6,0,0,'Have you laid waste to the demon strongholds?',64502),
(46297,0,669,0,0,'Is the way to the weapon clear?',64978),
(46769,0,6,0,0,'Have you found the wyrmtongue caches?',64502),
(46818,0,0,0,0,'I will hold this position. The spirits may be only echoes of their former selves, but they do not know that.',64978),
(46842,0,0,0,0,'No rest until the deed is done.',64978),
(47134,0,1,0,0,'We must stop High Inquisitor Raalgar!',64978),
(47224,0,66,0,0,'Today marks the beginning of the Legion\'s downfall.',64978),
(47238,0,1,0,0,'Such a task I cannot undertake alone. Your help is greatly appreciated, $n.',64978),
(47725,0,0,0,0,'Without the power of the seal we cannot bypass my wards.',64978),
(47726,0,0,0,0,'Without the power of the seal we cannot bypass my wards.',0),
(47727,0,0,0,0,'Without the power of the seal we cannot bypass my wards.',0),
(47855,0,0,0,0,'Memory roots me in place, more surely than the heaviest stone.',64978),
(47992,0,1,0,0,'The Legion\'s defeat here is inevitable now. We just need to see it through.',64978),
(48202,0,669,0,0,'The camp lies to the northeast.$b$bIt may appear hidden at first glance, but you can find the Light shining in the darkest places.',64978),
(48272,0,0,0,0,'It\'s a lot to take in, I know, but it might help us while we can still be helped.',64978),
(48280,0,0,0,0,'Eonar\'s still out there somewhere, but I don\'t know how much longer she\'ll last.',64978),
(48345,0,0,0,0,'We cannot know peace while Talgath hunts us.',64978),
(48461,0,1,0,0,'No demon is safe while I draw breath.',64978),
(48542,0,0,0,0,'',64978),
(48605,0,1,0,0,'The Legion must fall.',64978),
(48635,0,0,0,0,'Many of my brethren are deeply touched by shadow. It will take a tremendous effort to free them. Will you help?',0),
(48636,0,0,0,0,'War is costly work. Have you gathered additional supplies for our efforts here?',0),
(48641,0,0,0,0,'Return to me when you have finished aiding the Armies of Legionfall, $n.',64502),
(48668,0,0,0,0,'Grand Artificer Romuul is a reliable soul. We would be lost on this planet without him.',64978),
(48910,0,0,0,0,'This desolate place offers little for my people. Every hour is spent scraping together enough to survive. If I had more resources, I could offer you a ridgestalker.\n\nI can only part with a Krokul-Ridgestalker for this few resources once per week. Next week, I will offer you this trade again.',0),
(48911,0,0,0,0,'If you bring the necessary supplies, I can begin the distillation process, $n.\n\nI can only free one of the Void-Touched with this few resources once per week.',0),
(48912,0,0,0,0,'The campaign against the Legion has taxed our existing resources heavily. Bring me supplies and I will place a lightforged under your command.\n\nI can only spare a lightforged for this few resources once per week.',0),
(49014,0,1,0,0,'We have not come this far to stop now.',64978),
(49075,0,0,0,0,'Without the runes, we must face Sargeras\' army head on.',64978),
(49076,0,0,0,0,'Without the runes, we must face Sargeras\' army head on.',0),
(49133,0,0,0,0,'Have you located the sigils?',0),
(49134,0,0,0,0,'Have you located the sigils?',64978),
(49135,0,0,0,0,'Have you located the sigils?',64978),
(53761,1,1,0,0,'Befindet sich der Dreizack in Eurem Besitz?',62876),
(53762,1,1,0,0,'Die Krone ist in unseren Händen viel nützlicher als in den Klauen eines übergroßen Siltfressers.',62876),
(54058,1,0,0,0,'So eine Abwechslung kann ganz belebend sein, oder, $n?',0),
(54734,0,0,0,0,'I see my little helper found you just fine.',0),
(54735,0,0,0,0,'Have you found a suitable crew?',63834),
(54851,0,0,0,0,'I chose you for this honor to thank you for all you have done for my people, and all that you have done for me.',63834),
(56748,0,0,0,0,'Eat a sausage, drink some brew, then eat some more!',63305),
(57637,0,0,0,0,'Bring me the temporal anomaly as soon as you can, so we can get back to yesterday\'s problems tomorrow.',63305),
(82678,0,0,0,0,'Habt Ihr vielleicht etwas gefunden?',0),
(82679,0,0,0,0,'Have ye found anythin\'?',0),
(82706,0,1,0,0,'Dangerous exploration? Survivin\' by the skin of our teeth? Makes this ol\' dwarf feel alive!',63305),
(82817,0,0,0,0,'It brings me no pleasure, asking you tae fight against us. I feel for the bronze dragons and all the work they do tae protect the timeline.',0),
(83104,0,274,0,0,'Trust me, you can\'t miss it.',0),
(83105,0,6,0,0,'Do you have them? The smiths have been chewing my ear off.',0),
(83347,0,0,0,0,'By pressing ourselves to the extreme we can truly test our skills.',63305),
(83359,0,25,0,0,'Only the titans should reshape the world.',63305),
(83362,0,25,0,0,'I wonder what it is like to be covered in fur like a pandaren. I hear there are many floating places to visit in those lands. May they all stay afloat.',63305),
(83363,0,25,0,0,'Some of my people may see the arrival of the outlanders as an invasion, but I am glad it was you who landed on our shoes, and not the Burning Legion.',61265),
(83365,0,25,0,0,'Much has happened in the greater world while we worked in this place. I hear you had a hand in quite a bit of those tales.',63305),
(83366,0,0,0,0,'My people face a wide range of difficulties these days, as do yours. We can make the best of what\'s befallen us both.',63305),
(83436,0,1,0,0,'Any news are better than no news at all.\n\nDo not keep me waiting. Unlike the mountains, my patience is like that of a landslide.',63305),
(83443,0,1,0,0,'Let me know if you figure out what this darkness is all about.',63305),
(83457,0,1,0,0,'Any news I can report to High Speaker Brinthe?',63305),
(83458,0,1,0,0,'I am not sure if you are still here or already back.',63305),
(83459,0,1,0,0,'I know ceremonies are not your cup of cinderbrew. They are not mine either, but our job is important.',63305),
(83495,0,603,0,0,'Werft den Schalter herum!',62876),
(84286,0,1,0,0,'Fetch me the insignias from our Queen\'s guests and comrades. These have many uses within the city, and in exchange I will make you even deadlier to our foes within.',0),
(84370,0,0,0,0,'This map makes no sense... Champion! Good tidings I hope?',0),
(84371,0,0,0,0,'Xal\'atath war eine wahrlich rätselhafte Kreatur. Ich frage mich, ob der Hohepriester sich je ausgemalt hat, wie weit sie gehen würde...',62876),
(84776,0,0,0,0,'Beware of whatever lurks in these delves.',63305),
(84784,0,0,0,0,'Verschwendet nicht die Zeit von Lord N\'Zoth.',62876),
(85244,0,0,0,0,'The sooner we tackle the Underpin, the sooner we get me hat back!',61967),
(86151,0,0,0,0,'Place the Faceless Mask of the Burned Bridge on the altar.',0),
(86152,0,0,0,0,'Place the Faceless Mask of the Daredevil on the altar.',0),
(86153,0,0,0,0,'Place the Faceless Mask of the Dark Imagination on the altar.',0),
