(86155,0,0,0,0,'Place the Faceless Mask of the Long Night on the altar.',0),
(86363,0,0,0,0,'There\'s no need to hurry. But if you wouldn\'t mind hurrying anyway...',63305),
(86365,0,0,0,0,'If you lose those Carved Ethereal Crests, you can find more from powerful creatures around K\'aresh. I\'ve heard there\'s quite a variety of them!',63305),
(86503,0,0,0,0,'Speak with Xyggie Marou, do my tasks, and beat those Dastardly Duos!',61265),
(86801,0,0,0,0,'Place the Faceless Mask of Multitudes on the altar.',0),
(87328,0,0,0,0,'Are you ready to revisit these Horrific Visions?',61265),
